   <section class="home-left">
    <div class="intro-copy">
     <span class="intro-copy-lead">
      An oasis of attentive, individualized liberal arts education
     </span>
     <p>
      In your classes in Comparative Literature, the faculty will know your name.  We want to know what makes you unique. We want you to reach your highest potential. You will be introduced to new places, worlds, and times you have never known before.
     </p>
     <p>
      We are an intimate home and community for you to learn what you want to learn, with all the benefits of big Berkeley campus at your fingertips. Join us.
      <a href="/about-comp-lit/">
       <em>
        Read More
       </em>
      </a>
     </p>
     <p>
     </p>
    </div>
